Gully Boys Divine & Naezy’s ‘NY Se Mumbai’ Is The Song That Rap Enthusiasts Will Play On Loop!
Gully Boys Divine & Naezy’s ‘NY Se Mumbai’ Is The Song That Rap Enthusiasts Will Play On Loop!
You might be excited for Ranveer and Alia Bhatt's Gully Boy but it's real Gully Boys who are hogging the limelight for all the right reasons. The OG Gully boys have collaborated with Grammy-nominated rapper NAS for a brand new track.
Screengrab
For the uninitiated, NAS or Nasir bin Olu Dara Jones is the man behind eight platinum albums and has now collaborated for another exciting track.
Divine and Naezy are already in the news as their real story has inspired Zoya Akhtar's Gully Boy and their Aafat and Mere Gully Mein have become huge blockbusters.
Don't Miss 12.5 K SHARES 5.5 K SHARES 3.4 K SHARES 3.1 K SHARES 2.5 K SHARES
You will get to hear the promo track as it will release on Jio Saavan and is produced in collaboration with JioSaavn’s ‘Artist Originals’ campaign.
